<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>Insights on terrorism</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/188/insights_on_terrorism'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/terrorism.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
10 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>2h 21m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>It’s a solemn subject—one of the harsh realities of our world. Here, speakers with insightful thoughts on why terrorism continues … and what we can do to stop it.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

