<div class='copy text-left'>
<h4 class="h7 m5">The Terrorist's Son</h4>

<p><strong>by Zak Ebrahim, with Jeff Giles</strong><br>
The astonishing true story of an American boy raised on dogma and hate — a boy presumed to follow in his father’s footsteps — and the man who chose a different path. <a href="/read/ted-books/ted-books-library/the-terrorist-s-son"><strong>Learn more</strong></a></p>

